Description:
GOT A GROWING FAMILY? WE'VE GOT THE HOME FOR YOU
"That's right, it's a genuine five bedroom home in Officer."
Lavender Estate is quickly becoming one of the favourites among local residents. Being one of Officer's closest estates to Berwick means you remain within very popular school zones while being close proximity to the freeway and CBD access. It also means you're walking distance to local schools, public transport and within a few minutes drive from the proposed retail precinct.
Located within this burgeoning estate is the perfect family home. Built by Simonds, the two-storey home spans over 35sq under roofline and includes:
- 5 bedrooms, master with en-suite and huge walk-in robe;
- Formal living;
- Rumpus room;
- Light-filled open plan living/dining room adjacent to the kitchen;
- Modern kitchen with stone bench tops, butlers walk-in pantry and kitchen appliances including 900mm upright cooker;
- Ducted heating and cooling;
- Alfresco with decked area that neatly wraps around the rear of the home and invites you to explore the backyard;
- Double car garage with remote access;
- Great backyard with plenty of room for the kids to play.
Be sure to inspect.
